title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 69-5.8 - Periodic review
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 69-5.8 - Periodic review

State Regulations

For each approved rape crisis program, the department of Health shall perform on-site visits, review records or reports related to the program, and/or observe the training of rape crisis counselors as necessary to ensure compliance with the requirements of this Subpart. Notes
